LDK Solar to Spend $35 Million on Silane Gas Plant in Jiangxi

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-04-11T07:35:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-11/ldk-solar-to-spend-35-million-on-silane-gas-production-plant-in-jiangxi.html
LDK Solar Co., a Chinese solar
wafer maker, will invest $35 million to build a production line
to make silane gas at its Mahong plant in Jiangxi province,
according to a statement distributed by PR Newswire.     To contact the reporter on this story:
Feifei Shen in Beijing at 
 fshen11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
